{"id":"531223","title":"红楼一梦之贾兰","writer":"月离","dateline":"1557994705","updatetime":"1557994705","isover":"1","filesize":"1388633","linecount":"13319","wordcount":"448623","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-hQ4DWct/0/808e0098/Th/i-hQ4DWct-Th.jpg","hash":"honglou1mengzhijialan","urlhash":"kssq_5878abca5f34a3da1f98bbb3","sign":"","desc":"君子如兰,空谷幽香。【文耽美】贾兰，贾府的正牌玄孙，却是度日艰难，从小的生活，让他长成了不屈的性格。八岁那年，他遇到了改变他一生的人。十二岁那年，他遇到了能陪伴他一生的男人。各种风风雨雨，他依旧不离不弃的陪伴在自己身边，直到最后。【你的理想是什么，兰儿？】【年少轻狂之时，一人之下，万人之上。】【金戈铁马，征战沙场，那时的理想。】【现在呢？】【愿得一人心。】【白首不相离。】","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"14","suggcate":"轻,衍生同人,专情,日久生情,温馨清水,耽美,同人","suggcids":"14,115","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"0","isvip":"0","ish":"0","age":"古代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"0","list":"0,2oe,4xj,75r,9f6,c18,dn3,ffx,h9x,jpu,lyk,oi8,qm5,sux,uyo,wuo,z58,118t,134v,158g,173r,1922,1b13,1cst,1ecx,1frs,1hv8,1jt4,1lpv,1nmr,1pjq,1rua,1u48,1vwo,1xvv,1zs5,21q7,244l,26ga,28r9,2asb,2czv,2fez,2hei,2jis,2lvt,2o44,2q8m,2rwg,2tzf,2w3t,2ym0,30tl,32tq,34uv,36vl,38qy,3az6,3d7g,3fl1,3ie6,3ktq,3mtq,3p5q,3rdu,3tun,3wf9,3yjs,40cf,42ue,44ve,470a,494f,4asi,4d34,4f67,4gvb,4jgp,4lzi,4o09,4qyd,4t6p,4vii,4xza,509w,52ul,55bj,57c5,59ii,5bl9,5dku,5fy1,5ibf,5knv,5myn,5p0j,5r0k,5stc,5uq1,5wp2,5yuk,60j2,62sz,652z,67c6,69q7,6cdd,6ekh,6h38,6jlr,6ltn,6nn3,6pun,6rsi,6u4z,6weq,6y9e,707m,72lo,74nt,76un,799q,7b4q,7d2w,7fhz,7ha1,7in9,7k7a,7m3n,7nqw,7pmn,7ros,7tt3,7vul,7xej,7zht,81jt,83sa,860z,881q,89nt,8bku,8dur,8fm6,8hl1,8jo6,8lh8,8nbo,8pkn,8rnl,8tb5,8v5w,8wzh,8yza,90uw,92px,94x7,96wb,98lo,9ag1,9c6b,9dt2,9fi3,9hgd,9j5b,9kuk,9mkx,9o5z,9pdh,9qzz,9skq,9ul3,9wbt,9yp6,a0fh,a2b4,a4i2,a6bq,a8h0,aa4c,abtl,ady1,afvf,ahl5,ajcc,alo7,anja,apep,arim,at0x,aukq,awng,aycm,b0g8,b263,b46d,b65h,b8b4,baa5,bbth,bdju,bfo6,bhqu,bjlw,bllu,bncl,bpj9,brqg,btq7,bvt9,bxpj,bzvp,c1r8,c3ux,c5zt,c7xd,c9tc,cb3t,ccyi,cel0,cgdb,ci94,cjzy,cm47,co20,cq3n,crli,cteh,cvjt,cxdz,cz4h,d12c,d35l,d58e,d6wz,d8v5,dayt,dcm8,dedx,dgf6,digl,dkib,dm87,dnzp,dpdp,dr7u,dsvw,dumq,dwk4,dy7r,e0io,e2fp,e4g3,